#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.130"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.130:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.130:0.2"
msgid "13. Bhayavagga "
msgstr "13. Fears "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.130:0.3"
msgid "130. Cakkavattiacchariyasutta "
msgstr "130. Incredible Things About the Wheel-Turning Monarch "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.133, sc1
msgctxt "an4.130:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, acchariyā abbhutā dhammā raññe cakkavattimhi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four incredible and amazing things about a wheel-turning monarch. "

msgctxt "an4.130:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.130:1.3"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, khattiyaparisā rājānaṃ cakkavattiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "If an assembly of aristocrats goes to see a wheel-turning monarch, they’re uplifted by seeing him "

msgctxt "an4.130:1.4"
msgid "Tatra ce rājā cakkavattī bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "and uplifted by hearing him speak. "

msgctxt "an4.130:1.5"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, khattiyaparisā hoti, atha rājā cakkavattī tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr "And when he falls silent, they’ve never had enough. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.130:2.1"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, brāhmaṇaparisā rājānaṃ cakkavattiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "If an assembly of brahmins … "

msgctxt "an4.130:2.2"
msgid "Tatra ce rājā cakkavattī bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.130:2.3"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, brāhmaṇaparisā hoti, atha rājā cakkavattī tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.130:3.1"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, gahapatiparisā rājānaṃ cakkavattiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "householders … "

msgctxt "an4.130:3.2"
msgid "Tatra ce rājā cakkavattī bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.130:3.3"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, gahapatiparisā hoti, atha rājā cakkavattī tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.130:4.1"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, samaṇaparisā rājānaṃ cakkavattiṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "or ascetics goes to see a wheel-turning monarch, they’re uplifted by seeing him "

msgctxt "an4.130:4.2"
msgid "Tatra ce rājā cakkavattī bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "and uplifted by hearing him speak. "

msgctxt "an4.130:4.3"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, samaṇaparisā hoti, atha rājā cakkavattī tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr "And when he falls silent, they’ve never had enough. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.130:4.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro acchariyā abbhutā dhammā raññe cakkavattimhi. "
msgstr "These are the four incredible and amazing things about a wheel-turning monarch. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
#. VAR: cattāro → cattārome (mr)
msgctxt "an4.130:5.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro acchariyā abbhutā dhammā ānande. "
msgstr "In the same way, there are these four incredible and amazing things about Ānanda. "

msgctxt "an4.130:5.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.130:5.3"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, bhikkhuparisā ānandaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "If an assembly of monks goes to see Ānanda, they’re uplifted by seeing him "

msgctxt "an4.130:5.4"
msgid "Tatra ce ānando dhammaṃ bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "and uplifted by hearing him speak. "

msgctxt "an4.130:5.5"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, bhikkhuparisā hoti, atha ānando tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr "And when he falls silent, they’ve never had enough. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.130:6.1"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, bhikkhuniparisā … pe … sace, bhikkhave, upāsakaparisā … pe … sace, bhikkhave, upāsikāparisā ānandaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamati, dassanenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "If an assembly of nuns … laymen … or laywomen goes to see Ānanda, they’re uplifted by seeing him "

msgctxt "an4.130:6.2"
msgid "Tatra ce ānando dhammaṃ bhāsati, bhāsitenapi sā attamanā hoti. "
msgstr "and uplifted by hearing him speak. "

msgctxt "an4.130:6.3"
msgid "Atittāva, bhikkhave, upāsikāparisā hoti, atha ānando tuṇhī bhavati. "
msgstr "And when he falls silent, they’ve never had enough. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.130:6.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro acchariyā abbhutā dhammā ānande”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four incredible and amazing things about Ānanda.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.130:6.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.130:6.6"
msgid "Bhayavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.130:7.1"
msgid "Attānuvādaūmi ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.130:7.2"
msgid "dve ca nānā dve ca honti; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.130:7.3"
msgid "Mettā dve ca acchariyā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.130:7.4"
msgid "aparā ca tathā duveti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
